uid":152827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔買put/熊/沽期指?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻野長揸好似會伏 自己上網睇多d先好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32218ceea66317db032edda99471f3eea6753b6c","tid":552874,"uid":170027,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b799f55447b71cb476dd4c8ffd095a8fe5ffebfc","tid":552874,"uid":152827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:41:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔買put/熊/沽期指?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻野長揸好似會伏 自己上網睇多d先好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"你講緊有伏既應該係貢桿ETFs, 假設個市一日跌一升，打個和。但因為隻野係跟百份比 x 2, 所以蝕左。<br />\n<br />\n例：<br />\n<br />\n恆指10000點，第一日升5%, 第二日跌4.76%, 恒指變返10000點<br />\n<br />\n貢桿ETFs $10, 第一日升10%, 第二日跌9.52%, 得返9.9528<br />\n<br />\n而反向ETFs 法例定左一倍，所以我見唔到有呢個問題。"},{"pid":"801715db1f0a062417e32077c993095aab824162","tid":552874,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5833bf5db416f7205c28083d672f557f03e48b4","tid":552874,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"反向ETF - 熊市出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180206/57798054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F57798054&d=gcwCLdnYsGG3nWdkoZNjkAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9b848763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180206%2F57798054&h=ee93a5eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180206/57798054</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日Old news<br />\n<br />\n港股大瀉，除了市場上熱門的熊證、put輪錄得升幅，多隻反向EFT亦同樣告捷，FI未來恆指（7336）、FI三星恆指（7312）及FI華夏恆指（7321）分別升5.19%、5.33%及5.3%。<br />\n<br />\n國指反向EFT表現亦同樣優異，FI未來國指（7362）及FI三星國指（7328）分別升5.35%及5.4%。而聯繫美股的XI未來標普（7322）更升7.82%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打買過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"同槓桿類ETF一樣，因為計日回報，長擺一定輸。特別係大波波時期。<br />\n<br />\n例子：假如100蚊反向ETF，第一日升10%，第二日輸10%，已經等於99，倒輸1蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打想知多d，可以google 台灣50反1，輸到個邊老散叫救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9454aef2740fe495e84e92dbc831ded360fa6d","tid":552874,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"如果即日走貨嘅話，問題唔大嘅，只會有跟唔跟得足嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad45812c3adc3f8bbc06bb168544b2662eec9ad9","tid":552874,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"例如隻7336<br />\n<br />\n一年內持續收費+管理費=1.28+0.65%=1.93%，一年已經唔見接近2%。<br />\n<br />\n佢用期貨對沖，高水轉倉嘅話係有so嘅，但每年總會有幾個月低水轉倉（派息月），按手邊資料恆指股息率推算，2.8%左右。一年會唔見4.8%如果指數一直橫行。<br />\n<br />\n所以這種產品只適合本小老散玩即日對沖。如夠錢做按金請轉用小期對沖。"},{"pid":"1ad0a718bdf9b5c1eae8c92f0721c41a9f69b13a","tid":552874,"uid":150954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"667934e3c3c9bef41a5195aa454c03a249005b14","tid":552874,"uid":65622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad45812c3adc3f8bbc06bb168544b2662eec9ad9","tid":552874,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"例如隻7336<br />\n<br />\n一年內持續收費+管理費=1.28+0.65%=1.93%，一年已經唔見接近2%。<br />\n<br />\n佢用期貨對沖，高水轉倉嘅話係有so嘅，但每年總會有幾個月低水轉倉（派息月），按手邊資料恆指股息率推算，2.8%左右。一年會唔見4.8%如果指數一直橫行。<br />\n<br />\n所以這種產品只適合本小老散玩即日對沖。如夠錢做按金請轉用小期對沖。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:37:50.000Z","msg":"呢類産品會唔會好似XIV咁單日跌過80%就要除牌？"},{"pid":"b27c037f71ab5ddb93ab04903fe3b6e2b316b153","tid":552874,"uid":125976,"like":0,"di